    <h3 style="margin-top: 0">About these specimen(s)</h3>
    <p>
        I purchased this particular calculator from a seller on eBay in
        Illinois. It was clearly well-used before I obtained it; there is
        a name scratched below the SN and the hinge is rather unpleasent
        with time. Regardless, with some new 'N' cells (Not exactly
        standard these days) it works like a charm.
    </p>
